summary: Classic Rock Soundtrack, Skyrim - Sounds.bsa file overwriter
descriptionHtml:
The older generation might appreciate this. Breaks the lore a bit but ef it, I\'m jammin\' Keep the six string hummin\'. 
It\'s the first time I\'ve done something like this, but I\'d like to share it. 
Just drop it in your \\data\\ folder, overwriting the current Skyrim - Sounds.bsa
NOTE: Keep a copy of your original. If you have a modded Skyrim - Sounds.bsa it will get rid of your custom sounds. (obviously, but just a warning.)
author: Deathvest
